snippet: Shows like “The Mob Doctor,” “The Neighbors,” “666 Park Avenue” and “Made in Jersey” include plenty of recycled stock concepts that are oddly paired with archetypal TV characters.
abstract: Concepts for many of the fall 2012 season's new television series seem to have been generated by randomly mixing and matching elements from older shows.
lead_paragraph: Shows like “The Mob Doctor,” “The Neighbors,” “666 Park Avenue” and “Made in Jersey” include plenty of recycled stock concepts that are oddly paired with archetypal TV characters.

headline.seo: TV Fall Premieres Illustrate Odd Pairings of Stock Concepts
headline.main: The Old Mix and Match Inspires New Fall Shows
headline.print_headline: The Old Mix and Match Inspires New Fall Shows
